Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Total time for Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to reach Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR

Name: Minimun time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION

Name: Total time it takes the Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to be done before Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER

Name: Minimun time to Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION grouped by case:BudgetNumber
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case grouped by the last value of case:BudgetNumber

Name: Average time from Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER in unsuccessful cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION Cycle Time in the context of the entire process

Name: Total time for Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case
